snippet.title: Seekers of Tokane | Gameplay Trailer (Closed Alpha)
snippet.description:
Welcome Seeker, the portal will open soon. Prepare to embark on a dangerous rogue-like adventure, collecting and battling fierce Nefties in epic turn-based combat.

To gain access, purchase an Aurorian NFT, or register for our VIP list for a chance to receive a code. 

▶️ VIP List Registration: https://app.aurory.io/seekers-of-tokane
▶️ Whitepaper: https://docs.aurory.io/aurory-whitepaper/
